module desktop

go 1.25.0

// The desktop supervisor runs the existing Go API server in-process, so it
// depends on the sibling server module via a filesystem replace. go.work is
// gitignored in this repo, so the replace directive (committed) is the
// load-bearing module wiring for both local builds and CI.
